<h4 id="ID-9120e950-9fbb-4b02-ac8a-dc2e581ae5c3">Load u2l into a org document</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org9087ec7">
<p>
url2org function for importing info from the web
<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/emacs/comments/i2ep98/comment/g06s9vg/?utm_source=share&amp;utm_medium=web2x&amp;context=3">source</a>.
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-emacs-lisp">(<span style="font-weight: bold;">defun</span> <span style="font-weight: bold;">url2org</span> (begin end)
  <span style="font-style: italic;">"Download a webpage from selected url and convert to org."</span>
  (<span style="font-weight: bold;">interactive</span> <span style="font-style: italic;">"r"</span>)
  (shell-command-on-region begin end
    (concat <span style="font-style: italic;">"pandoc --from=html --to=org "</span> (buffer-substring begin end))
   nil t))
</pre>
</div>
